          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "The swell might have started pulling into the point. I’ve got a flask of Rooibos tea, honey and ginger that I’m going to be taking down to the point to get excited. I meet a guy selling sculptures and we share some tea and assess the waves together. Chris is out there and he gets some fun waves - I decide that it’s worth a little longboard.",
