          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "The surf is fun. I get some little runners on Angelica. I manage to get a nice cutback or two in and a few little nose rides. Bryan and Chris come join and we are all hooting each other on. The swell starts picking up slightly and they all move up a little higher up the point. I can’t join them as I’ve decided to add an another dynamic to the surf by not wearing a leash. As the swell starts building I realise two things: ",
            "link": null
